SELECT COUNT(1) FROM topic t 	LEFT JOIN user u ON t.user_id = u.id WHERE t.in_time BETWEEN %s AND %s

SELECT COUNT(1) FROM comment c 	LEFT JOIN topic t ON c.topic_id = t.id 	LEFT JOIN user u ON u.id = c.user_id

SELECT c.`id`, c.`content`, c.`topic_id`, c.`user_id`, c.`in_time` 	, c.`comment_id`, c.`up_ids`, t.title, t.id AS topicId, u.username FROM comment c 	LEFT JOIN topic t ON c.topic_id = t.id 	LEFT JOIN user u ON u.id = c.user_id ORDER BY c.in_time DESC LIMIT %s, 20
SELECT COUNT(1) FROM comment c 	LEFT JOIN topic t ON c.topic_id = t.id 	LEFT JOIN user u ON u.id = c.user_id WHERE c.in_time BETWEEN %s AND %s

SELECT c.`id`, c.`content`, c.`topic_id`, c.`user_id`, c.`in_time` 	, c.`comment_id`, c.`up_ids`, t.title, t.id AS topicId, u.username FROM comment c 	LEFT JOIN topic t ON c.topic_id = t.id 	LEFT JOIN user u ON u.id = c.user_id WHERE c.in_time BETWEEN %s AND %s ORDER BY c.in_time DESC LIMIT %s, 20
